description: Retrieves multiple analysis templates within a collaboration by their Amazon Resource Names (ARNs).

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the analysis templates belong to. Currently accepts collaboration ID.

parameters.name: analysisTemplateArns
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) associated with the analysis template within a collaboration. (string) ---

nested_items.description: The retrieved list of analysis templates within a collaboration.
